          <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
          <p class="lead">This Privacy Policy explains how HireHelper.ai (“HireHelper.ai,” “we,” “us,” or “our”) collects, uses, stores, shares, and protects personal data when you use HireHelper.ai, including our website, contact and project inquiry forms, help and support channels, account features, project collaboration features, payment-related workflows, and related services (collectively, the “Services”). This Policy should be read together with our Terms and Conditions.</p>
          <div class="legal-note"></div>
