<section class="legal-card" data-reveal><h2>1. Scope</h2>
<p>This Policy applies to personal data we collect from clients, prospective clients, specialists, contractors, service providers, website visitors, and other users of the Services.</p>
<p>“Personal data” means information that identifies you or can reasonably be linked to you, directly or indirectly.</p>
<p>HireHelper.ai is responsible for the processing of personal data described in this Policy.</p>
</section>
